Just kidding.

429
00:24:18,073 --> 00:24:20,273
Next week, we will ride a luxury train.

430
00:24:20,273 --> 00:24:22,273
And I'll compete with the queen.

431
00:24:22,273 --> 00:24:23,973
2 hours until the next station.

432
00:24:23,973 --> 00:24:25,873
A big showdown is going to occur,

433
00:24:25,873 --> 00:24:28,273
